snippet.title: Amber Heard stuns in sea green gown and talks female heroes
snippet.description:
Amber Heard appeared to take style inspiration from her queen of the sea character as she attended the star-studded world premiere for Aquaman at Cineworld in Leicester Square, London today.  Clad in a seaweed green gown and swimming cap style headwear, the 32-year-old actress was a vision of beauty as she stormed the blue carpet alongside her co-star Jason Momoa (inset) who also embraced the theme by carrying a gold trident. The film's storyline takes place in the wake of Justice League in which Arthur Curry/Aquaman, the half-human half-Atlantean ruler of Atlantis, reluctantly assumes the underwater kingdom's throne.
